<th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style=";;"><a href="List_of_writing_systems" title="List of writing systems">Types</a></th>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd hlist">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<ul>
<li><a href="Featural_alphabet" title="Featural alphabet">Featural alphabets</a></li>
<li><a href="Alphabet" title="Alphabet">Alphabets</a></li>
<li><a href="Abjad" title="Abjad">Abjads</a></li>
<li><a href="Abugida" title="Abugida">Alphasyllabaries / Abugidas</a></li>
<li><a href="Syllabary" title="Syllabary">Syllabaries</a></li>
<li><a href="Semi-syllabary" title="Semi-syllabary">Semi-syllabaries</a></li>
<li><a href="Ideogram" title="Ideogram">Ideogrammic</a></li>
<li><a href="Pictogram" title="Pictogram">Pictographic</a></li>
<li><a href="Logogram" title="Logogram">Logographic</a></li>
